reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Handy Little Case
reviews.reviewText: Got this case to go with my Jadens portable printer. I love my mini printer / labeler, but didn't really like carrying it around much because I was afraid it might get broken. With the case, now I don't worry. It's a nice and well made case. I love the mint green color I got. Incidentally, I have a PikDik Mini Portable Label Maker, as well and it also fits in this case, so I'll probably be ordering a seocnd one for it.
